    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation level for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 3. CFD model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. Note: boundary condition dataset (cpb-boundary-conditions-2025q4, vintage 2025-11-15) predates the February 2026 model revision; re-validation against updated boundary conditions is planned for the next assessment cycle.",
